    "created_at": "2012-05-24T16:49:01Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-05-24T16:49:01Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It [is documented](http://ipython.org/ipython-doc/dev/config/overview.html#configuration-file-location).\n\nSo instead of replacing `~/.ipython` with `~/.config/ipython`, which is true much less often at this point, it should be `IPYTHONDIR/`.  This substitution has been done elsewhere, but was apparently incomplete.  There is also no need to change the appearances in log output, which are in fact the output of a real run on OSX, where having a .config directory is highly unlikely.\n"
  },
